      "specialAbilities": "<!--thirdera-srd-hub-start:ooze.htm--><section class=\"thirdera-srd-hub\" data-hub=\"Ooze\"><h4>SRD type: Ooze</h4><p>\n\t<a href=\"/srd/typesSubtypes.htm#oozeType\">Oozes</a> are amorphous creatures that live only to eat. They inhabit underground areas throughout the world, scouring caverns, ruins, and dungeons in search of organic matter—living or dead.\n</p>\n\n<h3>Combat</h3>\n<p>\n\tOozes attack any creatures they encounter. They lash out with pseudopods or simply engulf opponents with their bodies, which secrete acids that help them catch or digest their prey.\n</p>\n\n<h5><a href=\"/srd/specialAbilities.htm#blindsightAndBlindsense\">Blindsight</a> (<a href=\"/srd/specialAbilities.htm#extraordinaryAbilities\">Ex</a>)</h5>\n<p>\n\tAn ooze’s entire body is a primitive sensory organ that can ascertain prey by scent and vibration within 60 feet.\n</p></section><!--thirdera-srd-hub-end-->\n<p><strong>Special Attacks:</strong> Acid, constrict 2d4+3 plus 1d4 acid, improved grab</p><p><strong>Special Qualities:</strong> Blindsight 60 ft., split, ooze traits</p><p>Imported from the d20 SRD; verify attacks and skills in-game. Full rules at d20srd.org.</p>",
